-- Bank of America shares pare gains after SEC charges
-- 
-- Mon Aug 3, 2009 12:55pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/08/03/us-markets-stocks-bankofamerica-idUSTRE57245A20090803

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of Bank of America Corp trimmed gains after the Securities and Exchange Commission said it charged the bank with making false statements in connection with the Merrill Lynch acquisition. 

 Shares were up 1.5 percent at $15.01. (Editing by Kenneth Barry)